Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向往天空 亲近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔于天空的神秘力量开始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有一个传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天之边际云之彼方存在着一片黄金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个故事讲述了一个追寻梦想自由生存的天空盗贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空盗团少年——酷的波澜起伏的爱和冒险的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.53,0:02:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.49,0:02:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是与人类同契后成为最强的武器的一种生命体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.79,0:02:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空盗团少年酷所遇到的少女蕾也是其中之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.87,0:02:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是传说中的七煌宝树之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.30,0:02:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此蕾被各种势力盯上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.54,0:02:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是酷为了把蕾送到传说之地——煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.95,0:02:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏上了旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行的同伴是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.41,0:02:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护翼的三人组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.36,0:02:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的真正目的还是个谜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.40,0:02:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里全部都是煌珠吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.88,0:02:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从世界各地集中起来的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.93,0:02:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的前辈们找到并保护起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.82,0:03:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的煌珠们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.16,0:03:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也...我也一定会保护你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.84,0:03:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.01,0:03:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 醒醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.24,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 天亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也 一定会保护你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也...我也一定会保护你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定...一定会保护你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.09,0:03:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五唱 那天的落泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路分成了两条啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.84,0:03:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点头绪也没有到底哪条通往村落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.35,0:04:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.07,0:04:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和奇雅走这条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.99,0:04:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带着他们两个走那条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.79,0:04:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天走下来没看到村落的话就来和我们汇合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们的路正确呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有几发照明弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.80,0:04:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天黑下来就打向南面的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.89,0:04:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到照明弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就去你们那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.65,0:04:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是前辈...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.89,0:04:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 叽哩咕噜个不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就是我们走这条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.10,0:04:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别磨磨蹭蹭地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.43,0:04:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到个村落 找到好吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.53,0:04:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希丝卡她想做的话一个人就可以保护好蕾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是我担心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.79,0:05:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈对于保护蕾的方针没有改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.72,0:05:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是为了强行从酷身边带走蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.84,0:05:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而和我们走了不同的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.05,0:05:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿是我多想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.43,0:05:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方可是七煌宝树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让达亚和摩杜去追啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人自己提出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.64,0:05:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们在拟煌珠中还算可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.27,0:05:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们嫉妒真正的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到七煌宝树不说完好地带回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.05,0:05:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起来也说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.12,0:05:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被那两个人干掉的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫蕾的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.55,0:05:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是七煌宝树的传言就是假的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅札兰斯一族的最终血统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.53,0:06:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然和一个无名小卒同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.91,0:06:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.06,0:06:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人做搭挡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.32,0:06:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这条路真的是对的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.61,0:06:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的运气向来不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.92,0:06:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么运气好的家伙会失去飞船茫然不知所措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之快点赶路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.16,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去不知什么时候能到守护翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.19,0:06:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.42,0:06:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是要去煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌珠乐园是传说中存在的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.22,0:06:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是煌珠们诞生的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知是否真的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.31,0:06:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.23,0:06:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾说要去的话我就一定把她送到那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我们煌珠完全保护协会而言...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先抢钱 再要人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些粗野的人是干什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.48,0:07:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一带的山贼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.57,0:07:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会保护蕾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是酷吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷德·望·朱鲁爱特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是力古吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 力古认识的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.07,0:07:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这些粗野的人是朋友吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 粗野...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.87,0:07:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙叫力古 以前同在一条船上当空盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和老大他们吵架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的飞船坠落了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.86,0:08:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事就别提了 力古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口气好大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.29,0:08:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来老大他们船上带着个煌珠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说那女孩就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.17,0:08:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害的武器弄到手了口气就大了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你真是太浪费了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.88,0:08:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.86,0:08:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.87,0:08:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会打到女人的 小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小...哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾 快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是小哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.27,0:09:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 先订正小哥的叫法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 别挡着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.96,0:09:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是那种人 但毕竟曾是同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.10,0:09:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.18,0:09:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.19,0:09:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙什么来头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.43,0:09:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 酷这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.50,0:09:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是个小毛孩为什么会和煌珠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌珠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.24,0:09:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐们 怎么了 在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.97,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正脑袋是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有力气就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叽哩咕噜地在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是核石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙难道是煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.64,0:10:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.14,0:10:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.66,0:10:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.43,0:10:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前的朋友做了很过分的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.68,0:11:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.81,0:11:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能教我用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.91,0:11:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.60,0:11:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才也没帮上什么忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.90,0:11:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想变强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.07,0:11:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想带蕾去煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此如果没有保护蕾的力量...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和蕾同契之后你不就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.15,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那么说没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.86,0:11:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.39,0:11:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.43,0:11:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害的武器弄到手了口气就大了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.07,0:12:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总在想 那样可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 不和你同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.98,0:12:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是她还是其他的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.32,0:12:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们守护翼的任务是保护你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把你们只当成武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.59,0:12:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护你们不落在坏人手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以一个普普通通的人的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.95,0:12:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里开开心心地度过一生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.63,0:12:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是把你们作为武器使用总觉得有点怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.17,0:13:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我不和你同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.31,0:13:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭着枪和体术可以完成任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.00,0:13:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你永远是朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.98,0:13:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂那眼泪的含义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是因为高兴而哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.39,0:13:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.68,0:13:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪是危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.25,0:13:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要学的话就教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微会有点痛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着想着就睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.34,0:13:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在想什么来着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.72,0:14:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 一想就困
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.05,0:14:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 蕾 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.26,0:14:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.18,0:14:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是希丝卡干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.85,0:14:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.93,0:14:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我拜托她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让我不用和蕾同契也能保护蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.29,0:14:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许应该尽快把蕾带到守护翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.21,0:14:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给酷的话太不可靠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.78,0:14:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.91,0:14:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.35,0:15:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.11,0:15:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.08,0:15:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.77,0:15:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.85,0:15:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是雷达上没反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.15,0:15:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拟煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.14,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先给我老老实实待一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.51,0:15:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们把那男孩解决了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把酷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接受的命令有两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住七煌宝树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.08,0:15:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走其同契者的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.39,0:15:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的性命...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌珠同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.57,0:15:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和煌珠同契的人一次只有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.81,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不死的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.73,0:15:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的主人就不能和那七煌宝树同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.13,0:15:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭那个就想打败我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.04,0:16:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的同契者当盾牌吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.54,0:16:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说同契者只是用来战斗的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便换多少都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.97,0:16:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人类把我们当武器使用一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.32,0:16:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按原路返回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和龙威他们汇合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.37,0:16:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭我们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 带上蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.75,0:16:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想当诱饵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的同伴被当成盾牌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.00,0:16:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.13,0:16:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能救出那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和他待在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.18,0:16:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.45,0:16:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希丝卡在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.33,0:16:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.77,0:16:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这儿 蜘蛛大婶们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.92,0:17:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过分 居然叫我们大婶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.94,0:17:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们又不是蜘蛛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是蜘蛛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠 给我下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.35,0:17:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对酷做了不该做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.40,0:17:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我提出同契的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.52,0:17:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果盯上蕾的家伙同时也要酷的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.64,0:17:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于刚才她们说的话很在意是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.98,0:17:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.42,0:17:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和酷分开也是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.11,0:17:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷说了不想和我同契的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.27,0:17:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为不想把你当武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.13,0:17:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那样只会使酷受伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.65,0:17:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你泪水夺眶欲出是因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.45,0:17:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得酷困惑痛苦的样子很可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.50,0:17:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那女孩流下的眼泪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.27,0:17:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 到哪儿去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.24,0:17:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.29,0:18:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.27,0:18:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么想在一起的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除同契了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.05,0:18:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算完成任务后将这个同契者也干掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.35,0:18:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖个交情两个人一起解决好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.55,0:18:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.19,0:18:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.90,0:18:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人类当盾牌的话 就你们而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽美星夜{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牵引之线{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.27,0:18:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此倾心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天之原{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追及之畏{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.42,0:18:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深藏在心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.09,0:18:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我共颂念{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.81,0:18:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气息相应{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缠绕飞旋之风{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝与我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远相随{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.93,0:18:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤诚之心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缠绕飞扬之风{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.38,0:19:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.29,0:19:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.09,0:19:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在由我来保护你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.09,0:19:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.23,0:19:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连结梦境{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连结各自梦境{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.37,0:19:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如我所诉{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.65,0:19:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清新之野{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风声飒飒{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.80,0:19:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连结梦境{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连结各自梦境{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.82,0:19:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚心诚意{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.22,0:19:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同契之后就这点水平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.79,0:19:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不值一提嘛 七煌宝树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强射击有个差池的话那个人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.06,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不争取点时间的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.92,0:19:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什么 这光...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.27,0:19:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在 酷 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强力无限{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.47,0:19:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连结梦境{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东风之钚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.81,0:20:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.78,0:20:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.90,0:20:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 愿意的话和我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.37,0:20:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不打算做山贼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.31,0:20:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我还有一定要做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.16,0:20:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.90,0:20:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从前就是说一不二的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.38,0:20:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.67,0:20:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 到了村落就开始特训哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.01,0:20:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.39,0:20:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是格斗术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.31,0:20:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所要做的是变得和蕾更默契地战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.85,0:21:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此而做的特训
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.83,0:21:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别啰嗦
